d":"c445972ed98aad7e1c703eaa4851ad2bcf5a6a64","tid":990562,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:37:12.000Z","msg":"今日先知原來個名係未久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d786482cd8c9a3fd68358c4b0e04aaec05a91aa5","tid":990562,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:40:49.000Z","msg":"樓主條廢物又出廢post"},{"pid":"7ff11cae1fdb37e88f06edd1a73a34f4fd8036f2","tid":990562,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25025a8e03a034b3629e3ae1c9f9cfe41ba168d5","tid":990562,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T16:36:12.000Z","msg":"農曆新年長假將至，港珠澳大橋將首次面對三地春運的「海量」出入境人流挑戰。自大橋通車後，三地口岸多次出現千人排長龍苦候穿梭巴士「金巴」數小時的亂象。為應付新春的客運需求，金巴已預先向跨境直巴公司借用超過三十部旅遊巴，並額外購置二十部新巴士，連同常設巴士合共投放一百八十八部金巴「應戰」。不過，旅遊業界仍不表樂觀，憂慮候車人龍會塞爆香港口岸，促運輸署在口岸分設旅行團及散客候車區域，以防混亂。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年十月通車的港珠澳大橋，交通安排混亂一直為人詬病。金巴營辦商表示，參考其他口岸以往於農曆新年假期期間錄得的跨境旅客數字，預計大橋旅客數目在該段日子將較平日及周末多，因此會加強服務，應付乘客需求。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新春期間，金巴除投放現有常設的一百三十八輛巴士外，將向跨境巴士業界借用超過三十輛巴士，並已購置額外二十輛巴士，將於農曆新年前後投入服務。金巴同時會因應三地的人流情況，調度車輛，應對「港珠線」及「港澳線」的旅客高峰時段。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，金巴表示會繼續提供團體預訂服務，鼓勵團體旅客透過預約或包車形式，乘搭穿梭巴士，相信有助管理各個時段的客流，避免團體旅客集中在同一時段進出。同時，亦會加派人手在口岸車站，協助維持候車及上車的秩序。&nbsp;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:46:05.000Z","msg":"you win"},{"pid":"c1f4055b56b020201cf83382f309b0fdf4eca01e","tid":990562,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:46:50.000Z","msg":"又要打丁了"},{"pid":"190fc789e27c5d1987371174dd61d23f24ba6496","tid":990562,"uid":99861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d786482cd8c9a3fd68358c4b0e04aaec05a91aa5","tid":990562,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:40:49.000Z","msg":"樓主條廢物又出廢post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:53:40.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"6459e6899e00ffb0c52b5719257a48741f9ebd32","tid":990562,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"我認我咸濕"},{"pid":"23c65fd9117041515f03639d5c25fb950781617f","tid":990562,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"我既大橋未久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a965da2b8f820392c0c8dd1a9b7a7ec11d029ea1","tid":990562,"uid":19289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e8362bd468b4289d7a4f06010be82f2006f943","tid":990562,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}